RA (April 2010). \"Statistical methods in genetics. 1951\". <i>International Journal of Epidemiology</i>. <b>39</b> (2): 329\u201335. <a href=\"/wiki/Digital_object_identifier\" title=\"Digital object identifier\">doi</a>:<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//doi.org/10.1093/ije/dyp379\">10.1093/ije/dyp379</a>. <a href=\"/wiki/PubMed_Identifier\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"PubMed Identifier\">PMID</a>&#160;<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/20176585\">20176585</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=International+Journal+of+Epidemiology&amp;rft.atitle=Statistical+methods+in+genetics.+1951&amp;rft.volume=39&amp;rft.issue=2&amp;rft.pages=329-35&amp;rft.date=2010-04&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1093%2Fije%2Fdyp379&amp;rft_id=info%3Apmid%2F20176585&amp;rft.aulast=Fisher&amp;rft.aufirst=RA&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMendelian+randomization\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Thomas2004-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Thomas2004_6-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\">Thomas DC, Conti DV (February 2004). \"Commentary: the concept of 'Mendelian Randomization<span style=\"padding-right:0.2em;\">'</span>\". <i>International Journal of Epidemiology</i>. <b>33</b> (1): 21\u20135. <a href=\"/wiki/Digital_object_identifier\" title=\"Digital object identifier\">doi</a>:<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//doi.org/10.1093/ije/dyh048\">10.1093/ije/dyh048</a>. <a href=\"/wiki/PubMed_Identifier\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"PubMed Identifier\">PMID</a>&#160;<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/15075141\">15075141</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&